desc_short	-----								[the Sequence] is a logic construction puzzler. Let your mind be your guide: Lay down seven different kinds of modules as your roadblocks to get you (portrayed as a binary data point) to a sweet destination. Apply an out-of-the-box thinking to get you to the next level!							
